class=\"ti ti-circle-check-filled text-[#4F46E5] text-xl\" data-kid=\"291\"></i> 3 Resume Scans / mo</li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-center gap-4 text-slate-600 font-medium\" data-kid=\"292\"><i class=\"ti ti-circle-check-filled text-[#4F46E5] text-xl\" data-kid=\"293\"></i> Basic Kanban Tracker</li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-center gap-4 text-slate-600 font-medium\" data-kid=\"294\"><i class=\"ti ti-circle-check-filled text-[#4F46E5] text-xl\" data-kid=\"295\"></i> Community Access</li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-center gap-4 text-slate-400 font-medium line-through decoration-slate-300\" data-kid=\"296\"><i class=\"ti ti-circle-x-filled text-slate-200 text-xl\" data-kid=\"297\"></i> AI Cover Letters</li>\n          </ul>\n          <button class=\"w-full py-5 border-2 border-slate-100 rounded-2xl font-black font-heading text-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-50 transition-all cursor-pointer\" data-kid=\"298\">Get Started Free</button>\n        </div>\n\n        \n        <div class=\"bg-white p-12 rounded-[40px] border-2 border-[#4F46E5] simple-elevation relative flex flex-col scale-105 z-10 overflow-hidden shadow-[0_32px_64px_rgba(79,70,229,0.15)]\" data-kid=\"299\">\n          <div class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-2 bg-[#4F46E5]\" data-kid=\"300\"></div>\n          <div class=\"flex justify-between items-center mb-6\" data-kid=\"301\">\n            <h3 class=\"text-[#4F46E5] font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"302\">Forge Pro</h3>\n            <span class=\"bg-indigo-50 text-[#4F46E5] px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"303\">Most Popular</span>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"flex items-baseline gap-2 mb-10\" data-kid=\"304\">\n             <span class=\"text-5xl font-black font-heading text-slate-900\" data-kid=\"305\">$19</span>\n             <span class=\"text-slate-400 font-medium\" data-kid=\"306\">/mo</span>\n          </div>\n          <ul class=\"space-y-6 mb-12 grow\" data-kid=\"307\">\n            <li class=\"flex items-center gap-4 text-slate-700 font-bold\" data-kid=\"308\"><i class=\"ti ti-circle-check-filled text-[#4F46E5] text-xl\" data-kid=\"309\"></i> Unlimited Resume Scans</li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-center gap-4 text-slate-700 font-bold\" data-kid=\"310\"><i class=\"ti ti-circle-check-filled text-[#4F46E5] text-xl\" data-kid=\"311\"></i> Unlimited AI Cover Letters</li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-center gap-4 text-slate-700 font-bold\" data-kid=\"312\"><i class=\"ti ti-circle-check-filled text-[#4F46E5] text-xl\" data-kid=\"313\"></i> AI Interview Simulator</li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-center gap-4 text-slate-700 font-bold\" data-kid=\"314\"><i class=\"ti ti-circle-check-filled text-[#4F46E5] text-xl\" data-kid=\"315\"></i> Priority Tracking</li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-center gap-4 text-slate-700 font-bold\" data-kid=\"316\"><i class=\"ti ti-circle-check-filled text-[#4F46E5] text-xl\" data-kid=\"317\"></i> Chrome Extension</li>\n          </ul>\n          <button class=\"w-full py-5 bg-[#4F46E5] text-white rounded-2xl font-black font-heading text-lg hover:bg-[#4338CA] transition-all shadow-xl shadow-indigo-100 cursor-pointer\" data-kid=\"318\">Start 7-Day Free Trial</button>\n        </div>\n\n        \n        <div class=\"bg-white p-12 rounded-[40px] border border-slate-100 border-t-4 border-t-slate-200 simple-elevation flex flex-col group hover:border-[#4F46E5]/30 transition-all duration-500\" data-kid=\"319\">\n          <h3 class=\"text-slate-400 font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-6\" data-kid=\"320\">Forge Elite</h3>\n          <div class=\"flex items-baseline gap-2 mb-10\" data-kid=\"321\">\n             <span class=\"text-5xl font-black font-heading text-slate-900\" data-kid=\"322\">$49</span>\n             <span class=\"text-slate-400 font-medium\" data-kid=\"323\">/mo</span>\n          </div>\n          <ul class=\"space-y-6 mb-12 grow\" data-kid=\"324\">\n            <li class=\"flex items-center gap-4 text-slate-600 font-medium\" data-kid=\"325\"><i class=\"ti ti-circle-check-filled text-[#4F46E5] text-xl\" data-kid=\"326\"></i> Everything in Forge Pro</li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-center gap-4 text-slate-600 font-medium\" data-kid=\"327\"><i class=\"ti ti-circle-check-filled text-[#4F46E5] text-xl\" data-kid=\"328\"></i> Expert Resume Review / mo</li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-center gap-4 text-slate-600 font-medium\" data-kid=\"329\"><i class=\"ti ti-circle-check-filled text-[#4F46E5] text-xl\" data-kid=\"330\"></i> 1-on-1 Salary Coaching</li>\n            <li class=\"flex items-center gap-4 text-slate-600 font-medium\" data-kid=\"331\"><i class=\"ti ti-circle-check-filled text-[#4F46E5] text-xl\" data-kid=\"332\"></i> Elite Networking Tool</li>\n          </ul>\n          <button class=\"w-full py-5 border-2 border-slate-100 rounded-2xl font-black font-heading text-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-50 transition-all cursor-pointer\" data-kid=\"333\">Contact for Elite</button>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <section class=\"py-32 bg-[#FAFAFA]\" data-kid=\"334\">\n    <div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6\" data-kid=\"335\">\n      <div class=\"text-center mb-24\" data-kid=\"336\">\n         <h2 class=\"text-5xl font-black font-heading text-slate-900 mb-6\" data-kid=\"337\">Common Questions</h2>\n         <p class=\"text-lg text-slate-500\" data-kid=\"338\">Everything you need to know about the Forge.</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"space-y-4\" data-kid=\"339\">\n        \n        <div class=\"bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm group\" data-kid=\"340\">\n          <button class=\"w-full p-8 flex items-center justify-between text-left focus:outline-hidden\" data-kid=\"341\">\n            <span class=\"text-xl font-bold font-heading text-slate-900\" data-kid=\"342\">How accurate is the ATS scanner?</span>\n            <div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-slate-50 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-[#4F46E5] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"343\">\n               <i class=\"ti ti-minus text-slate-400 group-hover:text-white\" data-kid=\"344\"></i>\n            </div>\n          </button>\n          <div class=\"px-8 pb-8 text-slate-500 leading-relaxed text-lg\" data-kid=\"345\">\n            Our scanner is updated weekly to match the algorithms of top tier ATS systems like Workday, Lever, and Greenhouse. We achieve a 98% correlation with actual hiring software feedback.\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm group\" data-kid=\"346\">\n          <button class=\"w-full p-8 flex items-center justify-between text-left focus:outline-hidden\" data-kid=\"347\">\n            <span class=\"text-xl font-bold font-heading text-slate-900\" data-kid=\"348\">Is my data shared with recruiters?</span>\n            <div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-slate-50 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-[#4F46E5] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"349\">\n               <i class=\"ti ti-plus text-slate-400 group-hover:text-white\" data-kid=\"350\"></i>\n            </div>\n          </button>\n          <div class=\"px-8 pb-8 text-slate-500 leading-relaxed text-lg hidden group-hover:block animate-fade-in\" data-kid=\"351\">\n            Never. We maintain strict data silos. Your profile, resume optimizations, and application history are visible only to you. We are not a recruitment agency; we are a tools company built for job seekers.\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm group\" data-kid=\"352\">\n          <button class=\"w-full p-8 flex items-center justify-between text-left focus:outline-hidden\" data-kid=\"353\">\n            <span class=\"text-xl font-bold font-heading text-slate-900\" data-kid=\"354\">Can I use this for non-tech roles?</span>\n            <div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-slate-50 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-[#4F46E5] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"355\">\n               <i class=\"ti ti-plus text-slate-400 group-hover:text-white\" data-kid=\"356\"></i>\n            </div>\n          </button>\n          <div class=\"px-8 pb-8 text-slate-500 leading-relaxed text-lg hidden group-hover:block animate-fade-in\" data-kid=\"357\">\n            Absolutely. While our examples often highlight tech companies, the ATS scanner and AI optimization tools work across finance, healthcare, law, and creative industries with high effectiveness.\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <section class=\"py-24 bg-white px-6\" data-kid=\"358\">\n    <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto\" data-kid=\"359\">\n      <div class=\"bg-[#4F46E5] rounded-[48px] p-12 md:p-24 relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col items-center text-center\" data-kid=\"360\">\n         <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top_right,rgba(255,255,255,0.2),transparent)]\" data-kid=\"361\"></div>\n         <div class=\"relative z-10 max-w-3xl\" data-kid=\"362\">\n            <h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black font-heading text-white mb-8 leading-tight\" data-kid=\"363\">Your Next Career Jump <br data-kid=\"364\"> Starts Here.</h2>\n            <p class=\"text-xl text-indigo-100 mb-12 leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"365\">Join 50,000+ professionals using CareerForge AI to land more interviews and higher salaries.</p>\n            <div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-5 justify-center\" data-kid=\"366\">\n               <button class=\"px-12 py-5 bg-white text-[#4F46E5] rounded-2xl font-black font-heading text-xl shadow-2xl hover:bg-slate-50 transition-all cursor-pointer\" data-kid=\"367\">Get Started For Free</button>\n               <button class=\"px-12 py-5 bg-[#4338CA] text-white rounded-2xl font-black font-heading text-xl border border-white/20 hover:bg-indigo-700 transition-all cursor-pointer\" data-kid=\"368\">Schedule a Demo</button>\n            </div>\n         </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <footer class=\"bg-slate-50 border-t border-slate-200 pt-32 pb-16\" data-kid=\"369\">\n    <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6\" data-kid=\"370\">\n      <div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-x-12 gap-y-16 mb-32\" data-kid=\"371\">\n        <div class=\"col-span-2 lg:col-span-2\" data-kid=\"372\">\n           <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-8\" data-kid=\"373\">\n              <div class=\"w-10 h-10 bg-[#4F46E5] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center rotate-3\" data-kid=\"374\">\n                <i class=\"ti ti-bolt text-white text-xl\" data-kid=\"375\"></i>\n              </div>\n              <span class=\"text-3xl font-black font-heading tracking-tighter text-slate-900\" data-kid=\"376\">CareerForge<span class=\"text-[#4F46E5]\" data-kid=\"377\">AI</span></span>\n           </div>\n           <p class=\"text-slate-500 max-w-xs text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10\" data-kid=\"378\">The AI-first platform designed to help high-performing professionals land their dream roles at record speeds.</p>\n           \n           <div class=\"bg-white p-6 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 mb-8 max-w-xs\" data-kid=\"379\">\n              <p class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4\" data-kid=\"380\">Join our Career Insights</p>\n              <div class=\"flex gap-2\" data-kid=\"381\">\n                 <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Email\" class=\"grow bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-xs focus:outline-none focus:border-[#4F46E5]\" data-kid=\"382\">\n                 <button class=\"bg-[#4F46E5] text-white px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-xs font-bold hover:bg-indigo-600 transition-colors\" data-kid=\"383\">Join</button>\n              </div>\n           </div>\n\n           <div class=\"flex gap-4\" data-kid=\"384\">\n              <a href=\"#\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white border border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-400 hover:text-[#4F46E5] hover:border-[#4F46E5] transition-all\" data-kid=\"385\"><i class=\"ti ti-brand-twitter\" data-kid=\"386\"></i></a>\n              <a href=\"#\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white border border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-400 hover:text-[#4F46E5] hover:border-[#4F46E5] transition-all\" data-kid=\"387\"><i class=\"ti ti-brand-linkedin\" data-kid=\"388\"></i></a>\n              <a href=\"#\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white border border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-400 hover:text-[#4F46E5] hover:border-[#4F46E5] transition-all\" data-kid=\"389\"><i class=\"ti ti-brand-github\" data-kid=\"390\"></i></a>\n           </div>\n        </div>\n        <div data-kid=\"391\">\n          <h4 class=\"font-black font-heading text-slate-900 mb-8 uppercase text-xs tracking-[0.2em]\" data-kid=\"392\">Platform</h4>\n          <ul class=\"space-y-6 text-slate-500 font-medium\" data-kid=\"393\">\n            <li data-kid=\"394\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#4F46E5] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"395\">ATS Scanner</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"396\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#4F46E5] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"397\">Resume Optimizer</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"398\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#4F46E5] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"399\">Cover Letter AI</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"400\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#4F46E5] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"401\">Interview Prep</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"402\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#4F46E5] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"403\">Job Tracker</a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n        <div data-kid=\"404\">\n          <h4 class=\"font-black font-heading text-slate-900 mb-8 uppercase text-xs tracking-[0.2em]\" data-kid=\"405\">Company</h4>\n          <ul class=\"space-y-6 text-slate-500 font-medium\" data-kid=\"406\">\n            <li data-kid=\"407\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#4F46E5] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"408\">About Us</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"409\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#4F46E5] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"410\">Success Stories</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"411\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#4F46E5] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"412\">Careers</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"413\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#4F46E5] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"414\">Blog</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"415\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#4F46E5] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"416\">Contact</a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n        <div data-kid=\"417\">\n          <h4 class=\"font-black font-heading text-slate-900 mb-8 uppercase text-xs tracking-[0.2em]\" data-kid=\"418\">Legal</h4>\n          <ul class=\"space-y-6 text-slate-500 font-medium\" data-kid=\"419\">\n            <li data-kid=\"420\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#4F46E5] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"421\">Privacy Policy</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"422\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#4F46E5] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"423\">Terms of Service</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"424\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#4F46E5] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"425\">Cookie Policy</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"426\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#4F46E5] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"427\">Security</a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n        <div data-kid=\"428\">\n          <h4 class=\"font-black font-heading text-slate-900 mb-8 uppercase text-xs tracking-[0.2em]\" data-kid=\"429\">Support</h4>\n          <ul class=\"space-y-6 text-slate-500 font-medium\" data-kid=\"430\">\n            <li data-kid=\"431\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#4F46E5] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"432\">Help Center</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"433\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#4F46E5] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"434\">API Docs</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"435\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#4F46E5] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"436\">Status</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"437\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#4F46E5] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"438\">Expert Coaching</a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"pt-16 border-t border-slate-200 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-8\" data-kid=\"439\">\n        <p class=\"text-slate-400 font-medium text-sm\" data-kid=\"440\">&copy; 2024 CareerForge AI. Built with precision for the ambitious.</p>\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl shadow-xs\" data-kid=\"441\">\n           <div class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500\" data-kid=\"442\"></div>\n           <span class=\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-600\" data-kid=\"443\">All systems operational</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </footer>\n</div>\n",
