" data-kid=\"46\">Applications</span>\n          </a>\n          <a href=\"#\" class=\"flex items-center space-x-3 px-3 py-2.5 text-zinc-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/5 rounded-lg group transition-all\" data-kid=\"47\">\n            <i class=\"ti ti-mail-opened text-lg\" data-kid=\"48\"></i>\n            <span class=\"text-sm font-medium\" data-kid=\"49\">Cover Letters</span>\n          </a>\n        </nav>\n      </section>\n\n      <section data-kid=\"50\">\n        <h3 class=\"text-[10px] uppercase font-bold tracking-[0.2em] text-zinc-500 mb-4 px-2\" data-kid=\"51\">AI Copilot</h3>\n        <nav class=\"space-y-1\" data-kid=\"52\">\n          <a href=\"#\" class=\"flex items-center space-x-3 px-3 py-2.5 text-zinc-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/5 rounded-lg group transition-all\" data-kid=\"53\">\n            <i class=\"ti ti-brain text-lg\" data-kid=\"54\"></i>\n            <span class=\"text-sm font-medium\" data-kid=\"55\">Career Advisor</span>\n          </a>\n          <a href=\"#\" class=\"flex items-center space-x-3 px-3 py-2.5 text-zinc-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/5 rounded-lg group transition-all\" data-kid=\"56\">\n            <i class=\"ti ti-vocabulary text-lg\" data-kid=\"57\"></i>\n            <span class=\"text-sm font-medium\" data-kid=\"58\">Interview Prep</span>\n          </a>\n        </nav>\n      </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"mt-auto pt-8\" data-kid=\"59\">\n      <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600/20 to-violet-600/5 rounded-2xl p-5 border border-indigo-500/20 shimmer\" data-kid=\"60\">\n        <div class=\"relative z-10\" data-kid=\"61\">\n          <div class=\"text-xs font-bold text-indigo-400 mb-1 flex items-center\" data-kid=\"62\">\n            <i class=\"ti ti-crown mr-1.5\" data-kid=\"63\"></i> PRO UPGRADE\n          </div>\n          <p class=\"text-xs text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mb-4\" data-kid=\"64\">Unlock unlimited AI resume optimization and priority matching