         </div>\n            <span class=\"text-xs font-semibold\" data-kid=\"53\">Senior Product Designer</span>\n          </div>\n          <p class=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 leading-relaxed italic\" data-kid=\"54\">\"Looking for a designer with strong visual craft and systems thinking...\"</p>\n          <button class=\"w-full py-1.5 text-[10px] font-bold border border-white/10 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors\" data-kid=\"55\">CHANGE ROLE</button>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"pt-6 mt-auto border-t border-white/5\" data-kid=\"56\">\n      <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600/20 to-violet-600/20 rounded-2xl p-5 border border-indigo-500/30 relative overflow-hidden group\" data-kid=\"57\">\n        <div class=\"relative z-10\" data-kid=\"58\">\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-2\" data-kid=\"59\">\n            <i class=\"ti ti-crown text-indigo-400\" data-kid=\"60\"></i>\n            <p class=\"text-xs font-black text-white tracking-tight uppercase\" data-kid=\"61\">Elite Plan</p>\n          </div>\n          <p class=\"text-[10px] text-white/60 mb-4 leading-relaxed font-medium\" data-kid=\"62\">Unlock precision AI tuning and 50+ ATS templates.</p>\n          <button class=\"w-full py-2 bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-500 text-white text-[10px] font-black rounded-lg transition-all shadow-lg shadow-indigo-600/20 active:scale-95\" data-kid=\"63\">GO PREMIUM</button>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"absolute -right-6 -bottom-6 opacity-[0.03] group-hover:opacity-10 transition-opacity duration-500 rotate-12\" data-kid=\"64\">\n          <i class=\"ti ti-sparkles text-8xl\" data-kid=\"65\"></i>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </aside>\n\n  \n  <main class=\"flex-1 flex flex-col aurora-glow relative\" data-kid=\"66\">\n    \n    <header class=\"h-20 flex items-center justify-between px-10 border-b border-white/5 z-20\" data-kid=\"67\">\n      <div class=\"flex items-center gap-6\" data-kid=\"68\">\n        <div class=\"flex flex-col\" data-kid=\"69\">\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"70\">\n            <h1 class=\"text-xl font-['Inter'] font-extrabold tracking-tight\" data-kid=\"71\">Resume Optimizer</h1>\n            <div class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 px-2 py-0.5 bg-indigo-500/10 border border-indigo-500/20 rounded-full\" data-kid=\"72\">\n               <span class=\"w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-indigo-500 animate-pulse\" data-kid=\"73\"></span>\n               <span class=\"text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-400 uppercase tracking-tighter\" data-kid=\"74\">AI Processing</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mt-1\" data-kid=\"75\">\n            <p class=\"text-xs text-white/40\" data-kid=\"76\">Comparing <span class=\"text-white/60 font-medium\" data-kid=\"77\">Original</span> vs <span class=\"text-indigo-400 font-medium italic\" data-kid=\"78\">Optimized (V2.4)</span></p>\n            <div class=\"h-3 w-px bg-white/10\" data-kid=\"79\"></div>\n            <button class=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-white/30 hover:text-white/60 flex items-center gap-1 transition-colors\" data-kid=\"80\">\n              <i class=\"ti ti-history\" data-kid=\"81\"></i>\n              Revision History\n            </button>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"82\">\n        <button class=\"group px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-bold text-white/70 hover:text-white transition-all flex items-center gap-2\" data-kid=\"83\">\n          <i class=\"ti ti-download text-lg group-hover:translate-y-0.5 transition-transform\" data-kid=\"84\"></i>\n          Export PDF\n        </button>\n        <button class=\"shimmer relative px-8 py-2.5 bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-500 text-white text-sm font-black rounded-xl shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(99,102,241,0.3)] transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5 active:translate-y-0\" data-kid=\"85\">\n          Apply All Changes\n        </button>\n      </div>\n    </header>\n\n    \n    <div class=\"flex-1 px-10 py-8 overflow-hidden flex flex-col gap-8\" data-kid=\"86\">\n      \n      <div class=\"grid grid-cols-4 gap-6\" data-kid=\"87\">\n        <div class=\"glass-card rounded-2xl p-5 group hover:border-indigo-500/30 hover:bg-white/[0.04] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 cursor-default\" data-kid=\"88\">\n          <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\" data-kid=\"89\">\n            <span class=\"text-[10px] font-black text-white/30 uppercase tracking-[0.15em]\" data-kid=\"90\">ATS Score</span>\n            <div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500/10 flex items-center justify-center border border-emerald-500/20\" data-kid=\"91\">\n              <i class=\"ti ti-bolt text-emerald-400\" data-kid=\"92\"></i>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"flex items-end gap-3\" data-kid=\"93\">\n            <span class=\"text-4xl font-bold font-['Inter']\" data-kid=\"94\">92</span>\n            <div class=\"flex flex-col mb-1\" data-kid=\"95\">\n              <span class=\"text-emerald-400 text-[10px] font-bold\" data-kid=\"96\"><i class=\"ti ti-arrow-up\" data-kid=\"97\"></i> 14%</span>\n              <span class=\"text-white/20 text-[8px]\" data-kid=\"98\">vs original</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"glass-card rounded-2xl p-5 group hover:border-indigo-500/30 hover:bg-white/[0.04] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 cursor-default\" data-kid=\"99\">\n          <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\" data-kid=\"100\">\n            <span class=\"text-[10px] font-black text-white/30 uppercase tracking-[0.15em]\" data-kid=\"101\">Keywords</span>\n            <div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-indigo-500/10 flex items-center justify-center border border-indigo-500/20\" data-kid=\"102\">\n              <i class=\"ti ti-key text-indigo-400\" data-kid=\"103\"></i>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"flex items-end gap-3\" data-kid=\"104\">\n            <span class=\"text-4xl font-bold font-['Inter']\" data-kid=\"105\">24</span>\n            <div class=\"flex flex-col mb-1\" data-kid=\"106\">\n              <span class=\"text-indigo-400 text-[10px] font-bold\" data-kid=\"107\">+8 Matching</span>\n              <span class=\"text-white/20 text-[8px]\" data-kid=\"108\">top relevant</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"glass-card rounded-2xl p-5 group hover:border-indigo-500/30 hover:bg-white/[0.04] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 cursor-default\" data-kid=\"109\">\n          <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\" data-kid=\"110\">\n            <span class=\"text-[10px] font-black text-white/30 uppercase tracking-[0.15em]\" data-kid=\"111\">Impact Level</span>\n            <div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-violet-500/10 flex items-center justify-center border border-violet-500/20\" data-kid=\"112\">\n              <i class=\"ti ti-target-arrow text-violet-400\" data-kid=\"113\"></i>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"flex items-end gap-3\" data-kid=\"114\">\n            <span class=\"text-4xl font-bold font-['Inter'] tracking-tighter\" data-kid=\"115\">High</span>\n            <div class=\"flex flex-col mb-1\" data-kid=\"116\">\n              <span class=\"text-violet-400 text-[10px] font-bold\" data-kid=\"117\">Strong Verbs</span>\n              <span class=\"text-white/20 text-[8px]\" data-kid=\"118\">action oriented</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"glass-card rounded-2xl p-5 group hover:border-indigo-500/30 hover:bg-white/[0.04] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 cursor-default\" data-kid=\"119\">\n          <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\" data-kid=\"120\">\n            <span class=\"text-[10px] font-black text-white/30 uppercase tracking-[0.15em]\" data-kid=\"121\">Formatting</span>\n            <div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-blue-500/10 flex items-center justify-center border border-blue-500/20\" data-kid=\"122\">\n              <i class=\"ti ti-device-floppy text-blue-400\" data-kid=\"123\"></i>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"flex items-end gap-3\" data-kid=\"124\">\n            <span class=\"text-4xl font-bold font-['Inter']\" data-kid=\"125\">A-</span>\n            <div class=\"flex flex-col mb-1\" data-kid=\"126\">\n              <span class=\"text-blue-400 text-[10px] font-bold\" data-kid=\"127\">Standard</span>\n              <span class=\"text-white/20 text-[8px]\" data-kid=\"128\">ATS safe</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      \n      <div class=\"flex-1 flex flex-col bg-[#111113] rounded-3xl border border-white/5 overflow-hidden shadow-2xl relative\" data-kid=\"129\">\n        \n        <div class=\"h-12 border-b border-white/5 bg-[#18181B]/50 flex items-center justify-between px-6 z-20\" data-kid=\"130\">\n          <div class=\"flex gap-4\" data-kid=\"131\">\n            <button class=\"text-xs font-bold text-indigo-400 flex items-center gap-1.5\" data-kid=\"132\"><i class=\"ti ti-eye\" data-kid=\"133\"></i> Side-by-Side</button>\n            <button class=\"text-xs font-bold text-white/30 hover:text-white/50 transition-colors flex items-center gap-1.5\" data-kid=\"134\"><i class=\"ti ti-separator-vertical\" data-kid=\"135\"></i> Overlay</button>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"136\">\n            <span class=\"text-[10px] text-white/20 uppercase font-black tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"137\">Compare Mode</span>\n            <div class=\"w-10 h-5 bg-indigo-500/20 rounded-full relative cursor-pointer ring-1 ring-indigo-500/30\" data-kid=\"138\">\n              <div class=\"absolute right-1 top-1 w-3 h-3 bg-indigo-500 rounded-full\" data-kid=\"139\"></div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        \n        <div class=\"flex-1 overflow-y-auto custom-scrollbar relative group\" data-kid=\"140\">\n          \n          <div class=\"absolute left-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-px bg-white/10 z-10 pointer-events-none\" data-kid=\"141\"></div>\n\n          \n          <div class=\"sticky top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-12 h-12 bg-[#18181B] border-2 border-indigo-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center slider-handle-glow cursor-ew-resize z-20 shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(99,102,241,0.3)] ring-4 ring-[#09090B]\" data-kid=\"142\">\n            <div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-0.5\" data-kid=\"143\">\n              <i class=\"ti ti-arrows-left-right text-indigo-400 text-sm\" data-kid=\"144\"></i>\n              <div class=\"flex gap-0.5\" data-kid=\"145\">\n                <div class=\"w-0.5 h-1.5 bg-indigo-500/50 rounded-full\" data-kid=\"146\"></div>\n                <div class=\"w-0.5 h-1.5 bg-indigo-500/50 rounded-full\" data-kid=\"147\"></div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          \n          <div class=\"flex border-b border-white/5\" data-kid=\"148\">\n            \n            <div class=\"flex-1 p-12 bg-white/[0.01] border-r border-white/5\" data-kid=\"149\">\n              <div class=\"max-w-xl ml-auto\" data-kid=\"150\">\n                <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-6\" data-kid=\"151\">\n                  <span class=\"px-2 py-0.5 bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/20 text-red-400 text-[10px] font-bold rounded uppercase tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"152\">Original Draft</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"space-y-6\" data-kid=\"153\">\n                  <div data-kid=\"154\">\n                    <h2 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-white/90 mb-2\" data-kid=\"155\">Senior Product Designer | Vercel</h2>\n                    <p class=\"text-sm text-white/50 italic\" data-kid=\"156\">Oct 2021 – Present</p>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"space-y-4 text-sm text-white/60 leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"157\">\n                    <p data-kid=\"158\">• Worked on the core dashboard and helped improve the user experience of the deploy pages.</p>\n                    <p data-kid=\"159\">• Designed new components for the design system and made sure they were used by developers.</p>\n                    <p data-kid=\"160\">• Collaborated with product managers to define new features and user flows.</p>\n                    <p data-kid=\"161\">• Fixed a lot of UI bugs and performance issues in the frontend code.</p>\n                    <p data-kid=\"162\">• Used Figma and React for most of my daily design work and prototyping.</p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"flex-1 p-12 bg-indigo-500/[0.02]\" data-kid=\"163\">\n              <div class=\"max-w-xl mr-auto\" data-kid=\"164\">\n                <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-6\" data-kid=\"165\">\n                  <span class=\"px-2 py-0.5 bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 text-emerald-400 text-[10px] font-bold rounded uppercase tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"166\">AI Enhanced</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"space-y-6\" data-kid=\"167\">\n                  <div data-kid=\"168\">\n                    <h2 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2\" data-kid=\"169\">Senior Product Designer | Vercel</h2>\n                    <p class=\"text-sm text-white/40 italic\" data-kid=\"170\">Oct 2021 – Present</p>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"space-y-4 text-sm text-white/80 leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"171\">\n                    <div class=\"optimized-highlight p-3 rounded-lg\" data-kid=\"172\">\n                      <p data-kid=\"173\">• <span class=\"text-emerald-400 font-semibold italic\" data-kid=\"174\">Architected and spearheaded</span> the redesign of core deployment dashboards, resulting in a <span class=\"text-emerald-400 font-bold underline decoration-emerald-500/30\" data-kid=\"175\">32% increase in developer productivity</span> and a reduction in churn.</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"optimized-highlight p-3 rounded-lg\" data-kid=\"176\">\n                      <p data-kid=\"177\">• <span class=\"text-emerald-400 font-semibold italic\" data-kid=\"178\">Engineered 50+ reusable components</span> for the global Design System (Geist), ensuring pixel-perfect parity and <span class=\"text-emerald-400 font-bold\" data-kid=\"179\">accelerating UI delivery speeds by 40%</span>.</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"p-3 bg-white/5 border-l-2 border-white/20 rounded-lg\" data-kid=\"180\">\n                      <p data-kid=\"181\">• Partnered with Product Leadership to define strategic roadmaps and complex user flows, translating business goals into intuitive design patterns.</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"optimized-highlight p-3 rounded-lg\" data-kid=\"182\">\n                      <p data-kid=\"183\">• Optimized frontend performance by auditing React render cycles, <span class=\"text-emerald-400 font-semibold italic\" data-kid=\"184\">eliminating 150+ UI bottlenecks</span> and improving FCP by 1.2s.</p>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          \n          <div class=\"flex border-b border-white/5\" data-kid=\"185\">\n            \n            <div class=\"flex-1 p-12 bg-white/[0.01] border-r border-white/5\" data-kid=\"186\">\n              <div class=\"max-w-xl ml-auto\" data-kid=\"187\">\n                <div class=\"space-y-6\" data-kid=\"188\">\n                  <div data-kid=\"189\">\n                    <h2 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-white/90 mb-2\" data-kid=\"190\">UI/UX Designer | Linear (Contract)</h2>\n                    <p class=\"text-sm text-white/50 italic\" data-kid=\"191\">Jan 2021 – Sept 2021</p>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"space-y-4 text-sm text-white/60 leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"192\">\n                    <p data-kid=\"193\">• Responsible for redesigning the issue tracking interface to make it faster.</p>\n                    <p data-kid=\"194\">• Created icons and illustrations for the landing pages.</p>\n                    <p data-kid=\"195\">• Helped team members understand the new design language.</p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"flex-1 p-12 bg-indigo-500/[0.02]\" data-kid=\"196\">\n              <div class=\"max-w-xl mr-auto\" data-kid=\"197\">\n                <div class=\"space-y-6\" data-kid=\"198\">\n                  <div data-kid=\"199\">\n                    <h2 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2\" data-kid=\"200\">UI/UX Designer | Linear (Contract)</h2>\n                    <p class=\"text-sm text-white/40 italic\" data-kid=\"201\">Jan 2021 – Sept 2021</p>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"space-y-4 text-sm text-white/80 leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"202\">\n                    <div class=\"optimized-highlight p-3 rounded-lg\" data-kid=\"203\">\n                      <p data-kid=\"204\">• <span class=\"text-emerald-400 font-semibold italic\" data-kid=\"205\">Pioneered a keyboard-first navigation paradigm</span> for issue tracking, reducing average task creation time by <span class=\"text-emerald-400 font-bold\" data-kid=\"206\">18 seconds</span>.</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"p-3 bg-white/5 border-l-2 border-white/20 rounded-lg\" data-kid=\"207\">\n                      <p data-kid=\"208\">• <span class=\"text-white font-medium\" data-kid=\"209\">Produced 200+ high-fidelity vector assets</span> and a custom iconography set, standardizing Linear's brand presence across all global marketing surfaces.</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"p-3 bg-white/5 border-l-2 border-white/20 rounded-lg\" data-kid=\"210\">\n                      <p data-kid=\"211\">• Mentored a team of junior staff on the \"Linear Method\" of product delivery, fostering a culture of high-velocity excellence and <span class=\"text-white font-medium\" data-kid=\"212\">streamlining multi-team documentation workflows</span>.</p>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        \n        <div class=\"h-16 border-t border-white/5 bg-[#0d0d0f] flex items-center justify-between px-10 z-30\" data-kid=\"213\">\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-8\" data-kid=\"214\">\n            <div class=\"flex flex-col\" data-kid=\"215\">\n              <span class=\"text-[8px] font-black text-white/30 uppercase tracking-[0.2em]\" data-kid=\"216\">Active Comparison</span>\n              <span class=\"text-xs text-white/60 font-medium\" data-kid=\"217\">Work Experience (2 of 4 sections)</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"h-8 w-px bg-white/5\" data-kid=\"218\"></div>\n            <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\" data-kid=\"219\">\n              <i class=\"ti ti-check text-emerald-400 text-xs\" data-kid=\"220\"></i>\n              <span class=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"221\">Auto-saved to cloud</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"flex gap-4\" data-kid=\"222\">\n             <button class=\"px-5 py-2 border border-white/10 text-white/60 text-xs font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-white transition-all\" data-kid=\"223\">Discard Changes</button>\n             <button class=\"px-6 py-2 bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-500 text-white text-xs font-black rounded-xl shadow-lg shadow-indigo-600/20 transition-all active:scale-95\" data-kid=\"224\">Accept & Sync Resume</button>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </main>\n</div>\n",
